</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_269" id="133v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>, bischof zu Bamberg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir tun <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz
                        uns <expan>newliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>meldt</expan> ward, wie ein
                            <expan>behemisch<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>priest<ex>er</ex></expan> zu <expan>Grefemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> und sich da in <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        worten beweist und <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> hett, darumb man etwas
                        arkwons <expan>cristan<ex>n</ex></expan> glawben antreffend zu im hett.
                                <expan>Ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>priest<ex>er</ex></expan> ist darnach zu uns in
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> stat <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und hat
                        sich bey uns niht <expan>priest<ex>er</ex>lich</expan> noch wol
                                <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan>, also daz er in
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> fenknuss <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        ist. <expan>Dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>priest<ex>er</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> schiken und haben auch
                            <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Mollitor <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>, mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu <expan>red<ex>en</ex></expan>. Et
                                <expan>roga<ex>mus</ex></expan> in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>
<expan>crede<ex>n</ex>cie</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>fest<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>penthecost<ex>en</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
